data.description: NO SHOWINGS! Beautiful three level colonial home located in a prime location. Offering a large and flat rear yard, this home provides you with plenty of privacy for your outdoor enjoyment. Completely remodeled throughout including new light fixtures, luxury vinyl plank flooring, a modernized gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops, a large central island, wall oven, cooktop, and vent hood. Tastefully designed primary bathroom with standalone tub, and tile floors. New Hot water heater, and new upper-level HVAC system. The bathroom is unfinished and awaiting your design!  There is water damage from both bathrooms upstairs which will require the bathrooms to be re-done and drywall repair in the ceiling on the main level (see photos).  **Property sold strictly "AS-IS" subject to third party bank approval.**
